## Tool-Use Protocol

1. Reason inside <think>...</think> tags.
2. Invoke one tool per turn using <tool_call> with JSON (keys: "name", "arguments").
3. Environment returns results inside <tool_response>...</tool_response>.
4. Reason again before the next action.
5. When done or responding to the user, use <answer>...</answer>.

Available tools:
